#: 007b6:8
msgid "Hinata-san, huh? I'd like to get to know her better. We do sit next to each other in class."
msgstr "Tengo que conocerla mejor. Nos seguiremos sentado juntos algún tiempo más."

#: 007b6:9
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Where's Hinata-san?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Dónde está Mizuki...?\""

#: 007b6:10
msgid "There were a lot of people here, but I didn't see her anywhere I looked."
msgstr "No la veo."

#: 007b6:11
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I wonder if she's...\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Podría estar...\""

#: 007b6:12
msgid "I had a feeling that she'd be outside."
msgstr "Tengo el presentimiento de que está fuera."

#: 007b6:20
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Knew it.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Sip.\""

#: 007b6:21
msgid "She was sitting there outside, all by herself."
msgstr "Estaba sola fuera."

#: 007b6:23
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Ah!......\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¡¡...!!\""

#: 007b6:24
# Revisar.
msgid "She recognized me and turned her head away. I ignored that and kept walking towards her."
msgstr "Me ha reconocido y me ha evadido con la cabeza."

#: 007b6:27
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What are you doing here?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Qué haces aquí?\""

#: 007b6:28
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"......resting.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"...Tomarme un respiro.\""

#: 007b6:29
msgid "Her response was curt. I suddenly had a thought: maybe she was just awkward around people."
msgstr "Me ha respondido a regañadientes."

#: 007b6:30
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Are you drunk?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Estás bebida?\""

#: 007b6:31
# Hay que ver si se refiere a que no ha bebido antes o a que no bebe.
# El japonés es muy ambigüo y los traductores al inglés no se esmeraron mucho.
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"I didn't drink.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"No he bebido.\""

#: 007b6:32
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You sure? Because your face sure is red.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Ah sí? Es que tienes la cara roja.\""

#: 007b6:35
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"I-it's the sunset.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Es por el sol.\""

#: 007b6:38
msgid "She turned her head away again. She might just be awkward, not a bad person."
msgstr "Ha vuelto a girar la cabeza para evitarme."

#: 007b6:39
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"...\""

#: 007b6:40
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Oh, right. I'm sorry about this afternoon.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Oye... Siento lo de antes.\""

#: 007b6:43
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Huh? What now?\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¿Qué quieres decir?\""

#: 007b6:44
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Remember? I called you a lesbian?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Lo de que eras lesbiana.\""

#: 007b6:45
msgid "Just having to explain that turned my cheeks red. What on Earth was wrong with me when I said that to her face?"
msgstr "Debo estar como una cabra por decirle eso."

#: 007b6:48
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"That really was horrible. Would you normally say that? Especially to someone's face?\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¿Cómo has podido decir algo así?\""

#: 007b6:49
msgid "Shit. I didn't mean to get her angry again."
msgstr "Ups, no quería hacer que se volviese a enfadar."

#: 007b6:50
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"S-sorry.\n"
"I guess I had the wrong preconception of an all-girls' school. My imagination went wild.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Lo siento.\n"
"Había oído que no era algo inusual en la escuela para chicas.\""

#: 007b6:53
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Your imagination? Oh come on! What the heck were you imagining?\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¿Dónde has oído eso...?\""

#: 007b6:54
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Well, it's embarrassing to say, but... I imagined two girls ****ing each other, ****ing their *****, and it was pretty realistic too.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Me habían dicho que las chicas hacían muchas cosas entre ellas...\""

#: 007b6:57
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Stop! Stop! I wasn't asking you go into that much detail!\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¡Para!\n"
"¡Ya es suficiente!\""

#: 007b6:58
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Huh? Oh, you weren't?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Está bien.\""

#: 007b6:59
msgid "Oops. I made her even angrier. Why do I always end up making her angry? Are we incompatible?"
msgstr "Ups. La he enfadado todavía más."

#: 007b6:60
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Hinata-san, are you upset that we boys enrolled at this school?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Estás enfadada porque no querías que ningún chico se apuntase a esta escuela?\""

#: 007b6:61
msgid "I wondered if that was the reason she was so grumpy. It was the only reason I could think of."
msgstr "Era lo primero que se me había ocurrido de por qué me ignoraba."

#: 007b6:64
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Not really...\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Eso no me importa...\""

#: 007b6:65
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No? But you're always grumpy? Oh, are you on your period?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Estás con la regla?\""

#: 007b6:68
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"............!\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¡...!\""

#: 007b6:69
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Er, no, nothing.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No he dicho nada.\""

#: 007b6:70
msgid "I really think I should just shut up."
msgstr "Creo que debería dejar de intentar hablar con ella."

#: 007b6:73
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Can we not talk about that? I hate periods. It's because I can't swim.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"No me gusta la regla. No puedo nadar cuando la tengo.\""

#: 007b6:74
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Oh, yeah...\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Ya veo...\""

#: 007b6:75
msgid "I guess I was pretty close?"
msgstr "Ya imaginaba que estaba enfadada conmigo y que no tenía nada que ver con la regla."

#: 007b6:78
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"I haven't been able to swim as much as I want to for a long time.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Llevo sin nadar todo lo que me gustaría desde hace bastante tiempo.\""

#: 007b6:79
msgid "She stretched out like she really hadn't worked her body in a while. Maybe she's just frustrated?"
msgstr "Se estira."

#: 007b6:80
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Why can't you swim? Oh, because your period came?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Y cómo es eso?\""

#: 007b6:83
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"You're wrong! It's because you boys came!\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¡Por vosotros!\""

#: 007b6:84
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Huh? Us? Why can't you swim because of us?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Nosotros?\n"
"¿Por qué no puedes nadar por nosotros?\""

#: 007b6:85
msgid "It had to be a false accusation, right? When I asked her, Hinata puffed out her cheeks. She looked just like an angry kid."
msgstr "Pone una cara de enfado como en los dibujos."

#: 007b6:86
# Revisar.
msgid "I almost started laughing."
msgstr "Hace que me entre la risa tonta."

#: 007b6:89
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Until now, I could swim wherever, whenever without worrying about it. The ocean is all around us after all.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Solíamos poder nadar siempre que quisiésemos.\""

#: 007b6:90
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"That's true.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Y?\""

#: 007b6:91
msgid "This was the perfect place for swimming. To put it differently, the ocean was all we had for fun here."
msgstr "Esta isla es un lugar ideal para disfrutar nadando."

#: 007b6:93
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"And well, there were only girls on this island, so I could readily swim without worrying about my outfit. I could just change wherever.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Nos podíamos poner el bañador en cualquier parte de la playa.\""

#: 007b6:96
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Now that you boys are here, I can't do that. I have to be more careful about a lot of things.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Ahora hay chicos por aquí.\""

#: 007b6:97
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I see.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Ya veo.\""

#: 007b6:98
msgid "She didn't have to worry earlier because it was an all girls academy, but she had to now that we were here."
msgstr "Ahora la entiendo."

#: 007b6:99
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I guess it is our fault then. I didn't know we were taking away your hobby. ...Sorry.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No éramos conscientes de que te hubiésemos fastidiado el hobby.\""

#: 007b6:102
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"You don't have to be that bothered by it. I'm not blaming you all, okay? But the fact that I can't swim is so fru~stra~ting!\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"No estoy realmente enfadada, ¿sabes?\n"
"Tan solo es que me gustaría poder nadar más amenudo...\""

#: 007b6:103
msgid "I see. So that's why she's always in a bad mood."
msgstr "Quizá estaba enfadada por eso."

#: 007b6:104
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"So you like swimming, then.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Te gusta nadar.\""

#: 007b6:107
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"I love swimming!\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¡Me encanta nadar!\""

#: 007b6:108
msgid "Hinata-san's smile was so fascinating it blew away all of her grumpy faces."
msgstr "Al final me ha mostrado una sonrisa."

#: 007b6:109
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Ah!......\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¡¡...!!\""

#: 007b6:116
msgid "We heard a clap of thunder and it started raining. It was an evening shower."
msgstr "Oímos un trueno. La lluvia empezó a caer."

#: 007b6:117
msgid "Then rain picked up force in no time."
msgstr "Es una lluvia densa."

#: 007b6:118
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Gah! Look at the rain! Let's get back inside!\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¡Volvamos dentro!\""

#: 007b6:121
msgid "But Mizuki refused to budge. She looked up at the sky and basked in the buckets of rain pouring down on her."
msgstr "Se negó a moverse."

#: 007b6:122
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Hey? Hinata-san?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Vienes?\""

#: 007b6:123
msgid "We were both soaked in no time. Our shirts, our underwear, even the insides of our shoes were wet. And yet..."
msgstr "Nos empapamos completamente."

#: 007b6:124
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Mmmmmmm!! This feels great!!\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¡Se siente genial...!\""

#: 007b6:125
msgid "Hinata-san stretched out wide and screamed with joy."
msgstr "Gritó."

#: 007b6:126
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Feels great? You're soaking wet!\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¡Pero si estás empapada!\""

#: 007b6:127
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"So what if I get wet? Rain is nothing but water.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Solo es lluvia.\""

#: 007b6:128
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I know, but...\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Ya lo sé, pero...\""

#: 007b6:129
msgid "Nothing but water. That's why getting wet was nothing. She had a point."
msgstr "Tiene razón. Nos mojamos cuando nadamos."

#: 007b6:130
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"That and it's too late now. We're not getting any wetter than we already are.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Ya estamos completamente empapados. Ya no nos podemos mojar más.\""

#: 007b6:131
msgid "She cast a glance up at the sky."
msgstr "Mira al cielo."

#: 007b6:132
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Heeeeeey! Pour hardeeer!!\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¡¡Con más fuerza...!!\""

#: 007b6:134
msgid "Sure enough, the rain got harder."
msgstr "Y empezó a llover con más intensidad."

#: 007b6:135
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Ahahahaha! It actually listened!\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¿¡Ves!? ¡Me ha escuchado!\""

#: 007b6:136
msgid "She was so happy from the rain that she was smiling from the bottom of her heart. Maybe this is the real Hinata-san."
msgstr "Sonríe y disfruta."

#: 007b6:137
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Haruma-kun, come over here and get wetter!\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Kazushi, ¡mojémosnos más!\""

#: 007b6:138
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I've never had a girl ask me to get wet before.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Nunca me había pedido una chica que me mojase.\""

#: 007b6:139
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Men shouldn't worry about little things! Come on over here!\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Venga, ¡¿o es que no eres un hombre?!\""

#: 007b6:140
msgid "She pulled me out from under the tree and heavy rain beat against me."
msgstr ""

#: 007b6:141
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Wow......\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Guau...\""

#: 007b6:142
msgid "Countless raindrops pelted my skin. It felt like each drop brought new life to me. It was incredible."
msgstr "Es como pegarse una ducha. Hace que me sienta muy bien."

#: 007b6:143
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"How is it for you!?\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¿¡Qué tal!?\""

#: 007b6:144
msgid "She spoke proudly, as if it was her doing. That childlike innocence was also quite charming."
msgstr "Su tono me está diciendo: \"¡te lo dije!\"."

#: 007b6:149
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Ah......\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¡¡...!!\""

#: 007b6:150
msgid "The rain quickly began to ease up, the clouds started to roll by, and in no time the rain had stopped."
msgstr "La lluvia amaina con presteza."

#: 007b6:153
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Awww, that's it?\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¿Qué? ¿Ya?\""

#: 007b6:154
msgid "She looked like a child being told to put her toys away. However, she still looked more satisfied than she was before."
msgstr "Lo dice como un niño que no ha tenido suficiente entretenimiento."

#: 007b6:155
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"That's a shame.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Lo siento.\""

#: 007b6:158
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Well-\n"
"I think I had enough for one day.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Bueno.\n"
"Con eso ha sido suficiente.\""

#: 007b6:159
msgid "She was drenched, but she put on a bright smile."
msgstr "Sigue mojada y sonriendo."

#: 007b6:160
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"That's right. You certainly have.\""
msgstr ""

#: 007b6:161
msgid "I flashed a smile in response to hers."
msgstr "Respondí a su sonrisa con otra sonrisa."

#: 007b6:164
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Ah!......\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¡¡...!!\""

#: 007b6:165
msgid "She finally realised that she was smiling at me and turned away."
msgstr "Al final se ha dado cuenta de que me estaba sonriendo y se gira."

#: 007b6:166
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You don't have to hide it.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No tienes por qué girarte.\""

#: 007b6:167
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"I-I'm not!\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¡No te estoy sonriendo!\""

#: 007b6:168
msgid "As the sound of the heavy rain disappeared, we hear a joyful ruckus coming from the cafeteria."
msgstr "Oíamos de fondo el alboroto de la cafetería."

#: 007b6:169
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"So, shall we head back?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Volvamos dentro.\""

#: 007b6:172
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Yeah, we should.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Está bien.\""
